parents.\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: WORLDSKILLS SINGAPORE  The restaurant and culinary operations graduate, who was up against 35 other competitors, had been training for this event for two years, and even returned to RP after graduation to train from 9am to 5pm on weekdays.\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 4169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4112, \"end\": 4114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Received_Pronunciation\", \"score\": 0.9530158292698463, \"rank\": 0.04928420630980917, \"text\": \"RP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Received_Pronunciation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Received_Pronunciation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the gruelling four days of competition, she had to provide food and drink services to guests in hotels and restaurants, displaying attentiveness and an understanding of their needs and expectations.\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This included demonstrating knowledge of all types of cuisine and dishes, as well as the methods of preparation and serving, along with the tools used.\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the competition,\\u00a0Ms Selina Sapii had to provide food and drink services to guests in hotels and restaurants, showing attentiveness and understanding of their needs and expectations.\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: WORLDSKILLS SINGAPORE  In the previous WorldSkills competition in 2022, Singapore won three golds, three silvers, two bronzes and 13 medallions.\", \"from\": 4721, \"to\": 4872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4767, \"end\": 4790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldSkills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WorldSkills competition\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldSkills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldSkills\"}, {\"begin\": 4800, \"end\": 